I '''Johann Nikolaus von Dreyse''' ([[Nobiembri 20]], [[1787]] - [[Disiembri 9]], [[1867]]) metung yang [[Germany|aleman]] a manimbentu kareng baril ampong iya mu rin ing gagawa kareti.  Bantug ya king kayang pamipalual a "[[Needle gun]]" inyang 1836,{{Fact|date=June 2008}} nung nu iti imapun de  ring  [[Prussian ukbu]] para agamit inyang 1841 bilang '''Dreyse Zündnadelgewehr''', o ''Prussian Model 1849''.{{Dubious|date=November 2008}}


